            'e.stat_box.1': '<div class="stat-number">132d</div> <div class="stat-label">protein · BGN 6.80 · without hunger</div>',
            'e.info_box.1': '<h3>Try</h3> <p style="margin-top:8px;">first Change only <strong>one meal</strong> today. The best start is: 3 eggs + oats + yogurt, instead of dough or jam. Don\'t diet. Make a strong breakfast.</p>',
            'e.info_box.2': '<h3 style="color:var(--red);">🏠 The take home rule</h3> <p style="margin-top:10px;"><strong>If it\'s not at home, you can\'t eat it in a weak moment.</strong> Environment determines behavior more than will.</p> <p style="margin-top:10px;">It\'s easier to resist <strong>once in the shop</strong>, than 20 times at home — after work, at 11:00 p.m., in front of the TV, after a bad day. Willpower is a limited resource. Don\'t spend it on things that you can solve with one shopping decision.</p> <p style="margin-top:10px; color:var(--muted);">You don\'t buy chips → you don\'t eat chips. You buy walnuts → you eat walnuts. So simple.</p> <div class="stat-pills mt-16"> <span class="stat-pill green">The environment &gt; will</span> <span class="stat-pill green">1 solution in store = 20 wins at home</span> <span class="stat-pill amber">Garbage is designed to be addictive</span> </div>',
            'e.info_box.3': '<h3>💊 Do you want to speed up the results?</h3> <p style="margin-top:8px;">Once the basics are in order—food, sleep, exercise—see which supplements are actually proven and how to take them.</p> <a class="btn btn-green" href="supplements.html" style="margin-top:16px; display:inline-block;">See add-ons →</a> ',
